{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015DdwiwYmdXiQVCKpK4gNBU","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package dsl\n     2→\n     3→type TokenType int\n     4→\n     5→const (\n     6→\tTokenEOF     TokenType = iota\n     7→\tTokenIllegal\n     8→\tTokenIdent\n     9→\tTokenString\n    10→\tTokenLBrace\n    11→\tTokenRBrace\n    12→\tTokenLBracket\n    13→\tTokenRBracket\n    14→\tTokenLParen\n    15→\tTokenRParen\n    16→\tTokenComma\n    17→\tTokenEquals\n    18→\tTokenArrow\n    19→\tTokenColon\n    20→\tTokenDot\n    21→)\n    22→\n    23→func (t TokenType) String() string {\n    24→\tswitch t {\n    25→\tcase TokenEOF:\n    26→\t\treturn \"EOF\"\n    27→\tcase TokenIllegal:\n    28→\t\treturn \"ILLEGAL\"\n    29→\tcase TokenIdent:\n    30→\t\treturn \"IDENT\"\n    31→\tcase TokenString:\n    32→\t\treturn \"STRING\"\n    33→\tcase TokenLBrace:\n    34→\t\treturn \"LBRACE\"\n    35→\tcase TokenRBrace:\n    36→\t\treturn \"RBRACE\"\n    37→\tcase TokenLBracket:\n    38→\t\treturn \"LBRACKET\"\n    39→\tcase TokenRBracket:\n    40→\t\treturn \"RBRACKET\"\n    41→\tcase TokenLParen:\n    42→\t\treturn \"LPAREN\"\n    43→\tcase TokenRParen:\n    44→\t\treturn \"RPAREN\"\n    45→\tcase TokenComma:\n    46→\t\treturn \"COMMA\"\n    47→\tcase TokenEquals:\n    48→\t\treturn \"EQUALS\"\n    49→\tcase TokenArrow:\n    50→\t\treturn \"ARROW\"\n    51→\tcase TokenColon:\n    52→\t\treturn \"COLON\"\n    53→\tcase TokenDot:\n    54→\t\treturn \"DOT\"\n    55→\tdefault:\n    56→\t\treturn \"UNKNOWN\"\n    57→\t}\n    58→}\n    59→\n    60→type Token struct {\n    61→\tType    TokenType\n    62→\tLiteral string\n    63→\tLine    int\n    64→\tCol     int\n    65→}\n    66→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01BgyGytUd79JrLbLZbPeM4r","session_id":"503a9c6b-ea73-4496-a067-8391d86da200","uuid":"298c3f05-aa54-4db3-9a35-28cc2297d62e"}
