{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Ud2EwbFNV7AFkqRGWXdX81","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"All tests pass across the entire project.\n\n## Summary\n\n**Root cause:** The DSL parser stores prompt values with the `file(\"...\")` wrapper (e.g., `file(\".cloche/prompts/fix.md\")`), but `handleAPIStepContent` was trying to use this wrapped string directly as a file path, causing `os.ReadFile` to fail silently.\n\n**Changes made:**\n\n1. **`internal/adapters/web/handler.go`** — Added `resolveStepConfigFile()` helper that extracts the path from `file(\"...\")` syntax before reading the file. Updated `handleAPIStepContent` to use this helper for prompt and script config values. Also added handling for the `run` config key (script steps use `run`, not `command`).\n\n2. **`internal/adapters/web/templates/project_detail.html`** — Updated the drawer's config display to strip `file(\"...\")` syntax for cleaner display, and added `run` to the list of displayed config keys.\n\n3. **`internal/adapters/web/handler_test.go`** — Added tests for `resolveStepConfigFile` (file() syntax, plain path, missing file) and integration tests for the API endpoint with both prompt files and run commands.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":875,"cache_read_input_tokens":42222,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":875},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"503a9c6b-ea73-4496-a067-8391d86da200","uuid":"97bec6fb-53e0-4034-bb7b-291ed9d9040c"}
{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":265121,"duration_api_ms":222075,"num_turns":30,"result":"All tests pass across the entire project.\n\n## Summary\n\n**Root cause:** The DSL parser stores prompt values with the `file(\"...\")` wrapper (e.g., `file(\".cloche/prompts/fix.md\")`), but `handleAPIStepContent` was trying to use this wrapped string directly as a file path, causing `os.ReadFile` to fail silently.\n\n**Changes made:**\n\n1. **`internal/adapters/web/handler.go`** — Added `resolveStepConfigFile()` helper that extracts the path from `file(\"...\")` syntax before reading the file. Updated `handleAPIStepContent` to use this helper for prompt and script config values. Also added handling for the `run` config key (script steps use `run`, not `command`).\n\n2. **`internal/adapters/web/templates/project_detail.html`** — Updated the drawer's config display to strip `file(\"...\")` syntax for cleaner display, and added `run` to the list of displayed config keys.\n\n3. **`internal/adapters/web/handler_test.go`** — Added tests for `resolveStepConfigFile` (file() syntax, plain path, missing file) and integration tests for the API endpoint with both prompt files and run commands.\n\nCLOCHE_RESULT:success","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"503a9c6b-ea73-4496-a067-8391d86da200","total_cost_usd":1.0693469,"usage":{"input_tokens":31,"cache_creation_input_tokens":33840,"cache_read_input_tokens":920053,"output_tokens":8181,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":33840,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":31,"outputTokens":8181,"cacheReadInputTokens":920053,"cacheCreationInputTokens":33840,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.8762065000000003,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":5573,"outputTokens":5